OL,3,CPolice 'told about death threats' days
OL,4,Cbefore mum killed in street
OL,6,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,7,FConduct (IOPC) has now launched an
OL,8,Finvestigation into West Yorkshire
OL,9,FPolice and Greater Manchester Police
OL,10,Fover contact officers had with Ms
OL,11,FAkter in the weeks before she died.
OL,13,FPart of the investigation will
OL,14,Fexaminer whether police were aware of
OL,15,Fany alleged breach of bail by Mr Masum
OL,16,Fand whether there were "missed
OL,17,Fopportunities" to safeguard Ms Akter.
