OL,3,CPolice 'told about death threats' days
OL,4,Cbefore mum killed in street
OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "We have been
OL,7,Finformed that West Yorkshire Police
OL,8,Fwere contacted on 28 March, when it
OL,9,Fwas reported Ms Akter had received
OL,10,Fdeath threats, and officers were
OL,11,Fdeployed.
OL,13,F"A search was carried out by the
OL,14,Fofficers in attendance but no suspect
OL,15,Fwas found.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
