OL,3,CPolice 'told about death threats' days
OL,4,Cbefore mum killed in street
OL,6,F"Evidence we have reviewed so far
OL,7,Findicates information was shared with
OL,8,FGMP around this time and our
OL,9,Finvestigation will include looking at
OL,10,Fwhat was known about any alleged
OL,11,Fbreach of bail, and the subsequent
OL,12,Fpolice response, including what steps
OL,13,Fwere taken to safeguard her.
OL,15,F"Our independent investigation will
OL,16,Flook at the nature of the police
OL,17,Fcontact with Ms Akter prior to her
OL,18,Fdeath, as well as the actions and
OL,19,Fdecision-making of those involved."
