OL,6,FMr Masum, who was arrested in
OL,7,FAylesbury, Buckinghamshire, has
OL,8,Fappeared in court charged with murder.
OL,10,FHe was remanded into custody, with a
OL,11,Fprovisional trial date of 18 November.
OL,13,FA 23-year-old man arrested in Cheshire
OL,14,Fon suspicion of assisting an offender
OL,15,Fis on bail.
OL,17,FFour other men arrested in Aylesbury
OL,18,Fon suspicion of assisting an offender
OL,19,Fand drug offences remain in custody.
