OL,3,CPolice 'told about death threats' days
OL,4,Cbefore mum killed in street
OL,6,FIOPC regional director Emily Barry
OL,7,Fsaid: "Our thoughts are with Ms
OL,8,FAkter's family and friends, who have
OL,9,Flost a loved one in tragic
OL,10,Fcircumstances, as well as all those
OL,11,Faffected by this deeply distressing
OL,12,Fincident.
OL,14,F"I would like to acknowledge and thank
OL,15,Fmembers of the public who were present
OL,16,Fat the scene and who tried to assist
OL,17,FMs Akter.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/7
