OL,6,F"It is only right that a thorough
OL,7,Finvestigation takes place to
OL,8,Funderstand the nature and extent of
OL,9,Fthe police interaction with Ms Akter.
OL,11,F"We have met with Ms Akter's family
OL,12,Fmembers to explain our role and update
OL,13,Fthem on our investigation. We will
OL,14,Fcontinue to update them as our
OL,15,Finvestigation continues."
